Description
	This program creates two threads which shares one variable(counter). The access of this shared variable is secured using mutex lock. Thread 2 would not access shared variable untill thread 1 finishes its execution.

Steps to compile
[1] make
	compiles program ThreadSync
[2] make clean
	clean up 

Output 

[root@localhost UsingMutex]# ./ThreadSync 

Job 1 started

Job 1 finished

Job 2 started

Job 2 finished

